#id=1
#text=Last weekend , I got into my car to head to the grocery store .
#id=2
#text=The store I normally go grocery shop at is Safeway , with the exception of the few times I go to SaveMart .
#id=3
#text=But for this time , I headed to Safeway .
#id=4
#text=I grabbed a shopping cart and immediately went to the left of the store like I normally do .
#id=5
#text=I grabbed the bread items I needed along with any breakfast pastries I enjoy buying .
#id=6
#text=Like normal , I skip the first four aisles due to them being for personal care and pet care .
#id=7
#text=I buy my personal items elsewhere -LRB- such as shampoo , etc. -RRB- .
#id=8
#text=I then went down the beverage aisle where I picked up several Gatorades and bottled waters .
#id=9

#text=I then continue going up each aisle after the beverage one , where I would pick up my frozen foods , canned foods , snacks -LRB- such as chips and cookies -RRB- , and any other lunch items -LRB- frozen or non-frozen -RRB- .
#text=I then ended with the fruits and vegetables , where I picked up a bunch of bananas and about four apples .
#text=I took my cart to the lone open register after waiting for about five minutes .
#text=After purchasing my items , I went out to my car and packed my groceries into the trunk .
